steps.name: Given  The user is on home page of ds algo portal

Given  The user is on the tryEditor page and clicks Try here button in Deletion page
When  The user writes invalid code in the editor of Deletion page and clicks Run button from sheetname "tryEditorCode" and row 1
Then  The user should be able to get alert on Deletion TryEditor page
